Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.88,0:00:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ruby! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.66,0:00:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.79,0:00:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi! Look this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.38,0:00:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.09,0:00:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,HER TRUE CHARACTER REVEALED!\NMEIMI'S CRITICAL MOMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari. What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.91,0:00:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about the last contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.35,0:00:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to start taking\Nphotos now for the next contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.13,0:00:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful\Nin your school uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.57,0:00:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you're also beautiful\Nwhen you're playing at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.68,0:00:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Senorita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving now.\NSee you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,May I have a second of your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Neverland Toy Shop?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.34,0:01:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the big toy store\Nthat just opened...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...on Second Avenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.72,0:01:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know\Nthat there used to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...a small toy store there, Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.17,0:01:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...there was a very big tree there...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Until a year ago\Nthat was my father's store.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We had to let the store go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.13,0:02:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And you came here for help...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm all right with the store now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I need your help with the tree...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,...in front of our old store.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The tree is still there\Nas the new store's display.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently I remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.21,0:02:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...that I left my music box in the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I had lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you leave it\Nin such a high place?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.07,0:02:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was a child,\NI often climbed the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently I was going through...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.28,0:02:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...my grandfather's belongings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.02,0:02:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...remembered my music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.56,0:02:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be in the hole in the tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.97,0:02:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very important to you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. My grandfather gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a souvenir...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...from my grandfather's\Ntrip to Switzerland...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.99,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Since that time, he was\Ninterested in music boxes...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.20,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately after coming back...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...he opened his toy store.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.08,0:03:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.22,0:03:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,... I didn't know the story\Nbehind the music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.66,0:03:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was my favorite\Nthing when I was child.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I always had it with me,\Neven when playing or sleeping...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.68,0:03:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I misplaced it\Nwithout even realizing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So she wants to get it back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.17,0:03:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,She says it's a beautiful music box...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.84,0:03:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,...which plays the hymn,\N"Ye Fair Green Hills of Galilee."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi has asked\Nthe owner many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.99,0:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,...to return her music box...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.06,0:04:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.37,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We just opened the store.\NWe can't take on extra stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To others,\Nit may just be a music box.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.92,0:04:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But to me,\Nit's something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a job\Nfor the Mysterious Thief St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Hey, good morning!\N- Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.53,0:04:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You have something in your hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This method is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.18,0:04:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"Tomorrow night...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm going to Neverland\Nto retrieve a music box...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.95,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...which plays 'Ye Fair\NGreen Hills of Galilee.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.39,0:04:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,St. Tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.66,0:04:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A note of warning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, you're caught off guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Saruwatari...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.42,0:04:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you challenging me\Nthis early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.22,0:05:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.86,0:05:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch that!\NIt's a special photo of Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.76,0:05:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's just a regular...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asuka Jr.!\NDon't touch it with your dirty hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this thing with Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,...I only have eyes\Nfor the beautiful Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.29,0:05:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you even listening to me?! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I remember correctly,\Nat that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,...it was with St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back, Asuka!\NI took that picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi! What is that next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.72,0:06:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.79,0:06:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.87,0:06:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.24,0:06:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Seira...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...with the stuffed\Nporcupine, Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a stuffed animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.59,0:06:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I have to grow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.76,0:06:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...out of collecting\Nstuffed animals but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.60,0:06:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in trouble, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.89,0:07:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're too pushy, she'll hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Seira.\NYou saved me in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, now is\Nthe time to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In school, let's maintain...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Ruby is a stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And Asuka Jr. is still\Nhaving doubts about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let him provoke you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mice is the plural form of mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'll read...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,...from Aesop's Fables...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.90,0:07:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,..."The Town Mouse\Nand the Country Mouse."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- PIease listen to me carefully.\N- Meimi, I have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.92,0:07:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to buy\Nconcert tickets this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know why\Nthis bothers you so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.01,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...but do you want me to find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.28,0:08:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...if this is a real stuffed animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,...are nicer than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! We're classmates!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,For that reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...please go out on a date with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.42,0:08:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For what reason?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.62,0:08:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to take\Nanother picture of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...with the stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.27,0:08:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,May I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.34,0:08:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, I'm sorry, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how about\Nafter school tomorrow? All right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would you like,\Nrice balls or sandwiches?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,In the middle of this mess,\Nyou're talking about food?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.98,0:08:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.25,0:08:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...about the snack\Nfor tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.62,0:08:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...during tomorrow\Nnight's surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one would you like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.60,0:09:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither! Give me some space!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.95,0:09:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sawatari!\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.79,0:09:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go on the date after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Me-Meimi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.50,0:09:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! It's my lucky day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.71,0:09:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.42,0:09:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm asking\Nfor forgiveness! Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.63,0:09:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your date and warning note\Nare on the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It will work out somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We were able to manage Ruby...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...without too much trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.52,0:09:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was careless, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.75,0:10:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There are stuffed porcupines...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have seen one\Nat a toy store before.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a stuffed animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...with a music box,\Nand it looks exactly like Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.08,0:10:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We can buy it and fool Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not all!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.62,0:10:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The music that plays is also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.73,0:10:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ye Fair Green Hills of Galilee."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'm going to get\Nthe stuffed animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...that looks like Ruby!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.04,0:10:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I checked earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,...and it's out of stock now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of stock?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do, Seira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other way now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.64,0:10:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby, could you do me a favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.99,0:10:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you pretend to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.06,0:11:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...a stuffed animal\Nfor the rest of the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Eimi!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.41,0:11:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's another peaceful day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.49,0:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.66,0:11:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,TROUBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.40,0:11:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to take\NRuby to school, Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.47,0:11:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Ruby?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.48,0:11:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, Ruby seems\Nto have caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.25,0:11:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm thinking of\Ndropping her off at the vet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all! I'm going!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.59,0:11:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I managed to fool Dad and Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The harder part\Nis coming up, Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's hang in there all day today!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.03,0:12:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One hour later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.61,0:12:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hours later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.42,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After school!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Haneoka!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.70,0:12:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it going to be okay...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.78,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in our store,\Na music box with the hymn...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.68,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,..."Ye Fair Green Hills of Galilee"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,...is only sold with this item.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.98,0:12:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They're out of stock now...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.48,0:12:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...and we have only\Nthis one for display.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So this is the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.04,0:13:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...that St. Tail is targeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Whew! It's a big toy store!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be the tree\Nwhere the music box is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.85,0:13:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.29,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, we're having\Na grand opening sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So we can't close the store,\Nno matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I would like\Nto borrow something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.41,0:13:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,EMPLOYEE LOCKER ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.92,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Why do I have to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Asuka Jr. ...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.62,0:13:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This time your strategy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...is to disguise yourself\Nand then catch her, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.53,0:14:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.51,0:14:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sawatari! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know any fox.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.93,0:14:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing\Nin that costume?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I am doing this...\Nin order to catch St. Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.05,0:14:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But you do look good\Nin that costume!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.66,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.46,0:14:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough about me!\NWhat can you report?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a stuffed animal. Probably!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.75,0:14:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you can't see past...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.92,0:14:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...Meimi, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.99,0:14:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll look into it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Haneoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.06,0:15:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, it's a fox.\NCome on! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...if that's really a stuffed animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.95,0:15:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.33,0:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops. Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A smiling fox is\Nfalling down the stairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhhh, ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.51,0:15:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew the way\Nthat fox fell was familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.56,0:15:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! I've caught a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do, Seira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here she comes! St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you escape today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.93,0:16:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.17,0:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She just appeared\Non top of the tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.13,0:17:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,For me, it was pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.67,0:17:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,May the blessings\Nof God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.41,0:17:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for disturbing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...Show...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.79,0:17:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,...Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My store...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.07,0:17:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.48,0:17:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking the music\Nbox with the hymn...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.99,0:18:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,..."Ye Fair Green Hills of Galilee!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I thought there\Nwas only one music box...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.62,0:18:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she's gone...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.93,0:18:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You couldn't catch her once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did you get\Nthe one on your back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.82,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought it before\Nthe store was out of stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It's a stuffed animal...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.74,0:18:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.51,0:18:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.18,0:18:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than thinking too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.42,0:19:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...I should just catch her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.79,0:19:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,When I catch her...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...everything will become clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.78,0:19:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruby, I love you!
